http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/YSRC-flays-govt.-over-poll-promises/article13976661.ece

Senior YSR Congress leader and former MLA B Gurunath Reddy on accused the TDP government of failing to deliver on the promises made by them prior to the elections.Accusing the government of not implementing the farm loan waiver scheme in a meaningful manner, he said that the farmers had voted the TDP, hoping to rid themselves of debt completely, only to find out the ‘ill intentions’ of the government post-polls.“DWCRA groups have become indebted. Banks are harassing them to pay their dues and they have been taken off the development cycle completely,” said Mr. Gurunath Reddy.